s/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6904efea8e7a6ea6b8486a306abdce3febe4a1f","tid":446490,"uid":54901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"我都想辣辣聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b50bf144c13608f23820d3c13650cdc3dbe030d","tid":446490,"uid":3706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同問<br />\n想練listening<br />\n有無咩apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同技巧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nListening都好差<br />\n香港人講個啲先叫做聽得明<br />\n外國人口音+講快少少已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlistening 可以不停睇西片聽人地平時係點講野<br />\nspeaking 要靠你不停同人講先練到<br />\n同埋唔洗咁驚講，基本上識普通英文已經可以同人溝通到"},{"pid":"c11733623eb21def91c491fd410bdd47590ed122","tid":446490,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"有意學speaking <br />\n留名"},{"pid":"fc60f8cd7905bf14dc92fa29d1455571f1509b30","tid":446490,"uid":115306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"我想學grammar <br />\n寫email寫文成pat屎咁<br />\n好彩返工講多過寫"},{"pid":"f280e53e62b317b96347d4177ff916c52ecd5abd","tid":446490,"uid":18245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"或者比起知識 你更需要既係自信"},{"pid":"290122fff328e25d5c62d4d2987651f2891080d0","tid":446490,"uid":92420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>或者比起知識 你更需要既係自信</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講得好岩 我覺得自己咁無自信真係好拖累自己"},{"pid":"6079acf23333d80e857ffc68e773ccc5dd2a8fa5","tid":446490,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24