0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你調轉<br />\n反而grammar好差 writing成日卡住卡住咁</blockquote><br />\n分唔到幾時用咩tense <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇例子<br />\n其實英文最主要只係嗰九個tense<br />\n再加佢地嘅小小演變"},{"pid":"146fd17a3b988de65b1d5f2add40be9300e93c8d","tid":446490,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你調轉<br />\n反而grammar好差 writing成日卡住卡住咁</blockquote><br />\n分唔到幾時用咩tense <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇例子<br />\n其實英文最主要只係嗰九個tense<br />\n再加佢地嘅小小演變</blockquote><br />\n姐係如果故事形式 係以前發生既 咁固然用past tense<br />\n呢d簡單既我都明白<br />\n但係到寫封email 寫essay個d 就唔知應該用咩<br />\n例如would 同 will 幾時用 幾時用ing個d我都唔係好清楚<br />\n有冇高手指教下細佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5183ef6f2dc677db492b5b8d7593ba1964e7884","tid":446490,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你調轉<br />\n反而grammar好差 writing成日卡住卡住咁</blockquote><br />\n分唔到幾時用咩tense <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇例子<br />\n其實英文最主要只係嗰九個tense<br />\n再加佢地嘅小小演變</blockquote><br />\n姐係如果故事形式 係以前發生既 咁固然用past tense<br />\n呢d簡單既我都明白<br />\n但係到寫封email 寫essay個d 就唔知應該用咩<br />\n例如would 同 will 幾時用 幾時用ing個d我都唔係好清楚<br />\n有冇高手指教下細佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwould will幾時用呢<br />\nwould係will嘅past tense<br />\nreported speech都會將will變成would<br />\n另外有啲特殊用法<br />\neg i would like to xxx<br />\nwould like=want<br />\n不過呢個比較禮貌啲<br />\n<br />\ning 有幾個用法<br />\n第一個最普遍嘅 係continuous tense<br />\neg I am wandering.<br />\n另外就係present participle<br />\n同gerund"},{"pid":"300af9299672466bc01a7fa995b26f1c56653483","tid":446490,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你調轉<br />\n反而grammar好差 writing成日卡住卡住咁</blockquote><br />\n分唔到幾時用咩tense <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇例子<br />\n其實英文最主要只係嗰九個tense<br />\n再加佢地嘅小小演變</blockquote><br />\n姐係如果故事形式 係以前發生既 咁固然用past tense<br />\n呢d簡單既我都明白<br />\n但係到寫封email 寫essay個d 就唔知應該用咩<br />\n例如would 同 will 幾時用 幾時用ing個d我都唔係好清楚<br />\n有冇高手指教下細佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwould will幾時用呢<br />\nwould係will嘅past tense<br />\nreported speech都會將will變成would<br />\n另外有啲特殊用法<br />\neg i would like to xxx<br />\nwould like=want<br />\n不過呢個比較禮貌啲<br />\n<br />\ning 有幾個用法<br />\n第一個最普遍嘅 係continuous tense<br />\neg I am wandering.<br />\n另外就係present participle<br />\n同gerund</blockquote><br />\npresent participle<br />\n可能冇聽過但係成日出現<br />\n第一係用嚟做形容詞<br />\neg disappointing, boring, surprising<br />\n第二個 我唔直接答你 我用例子答你<br />\nthe building is burning&gt;the burning building"},{"pid":"901d1aeb06039b020ca973d29bf17d5d72c105c9","tid":446490,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"唔敢講驚錯&gt;唔敢講驚錯&gt;唔敢講驚錯&gt;唔敢講驚錯&gt;唔敢講驚錯&gt;唔敢講驚錯&gt;loop<br />\n<br />\n要改左你心態先認真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7138f073d4b6528eb888cbb1a85b700ed373ef","tid":446490,"uid":8487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我寫作 grammar叫做好少少<br />\nSpeaking真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢講，又驚錯，搞到1999咁<br />\n<br />\n最近見工失敗，真係好想增值下自己（由其是speaking）<br />\n有無英文高手分享下心得<br />\n或者有無人join過類似English town啲課程？有無用？<br />\n好想講英文fluent 啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/Potatooooo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.